&lt;p&gt;But the phone giant had to scramble to keep the deal from unraveling after Yahoo disclosed two massive data breaches. The companies have agreed &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.wsj.com/articles/why-verizon-decided-to-still-buy-yahoo-after-big-data-breaches-1487679768&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.wsj.com/articles/why-verizon-decided-to-still-buy-yahoo-after-big-data-breaches-1487679768&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

