&lt;p&gt;Yahoo and Verizon on Tuesday issued a joint statement that the two companies have renegotiated their acquisition deal. Verizon agreed to amend the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/295553/data-breaches-force-yahoo-to-amend-verizon-deal-by.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/295553/data-breaches-force-yahoo-to-amend-verizon-deal-by.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

