&lt;p&gt;slashed the price of the sale of its core Internet business to Verizon by $350 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://heidelbergnigelheraut.co.za/afp/249943/yahoo-slashes-price-of-verizon-deal-350-mn-after-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://heidelbergnigelheraut.co.za/afp/249943/yahoo-slashes-price-of-verizon-deal-350-mn-after-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon Hacks $350 Million From Yahoo Deal After Massive Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The price reduction follow&amp;rsquo;s Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s disclosure of two massive user-data breaches affecting more than 1 billion accounts  months after the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://variety.com/2017/digital/news/verizon-yahoo-data-hacks-350-million-deal-1201992682/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://variety.com/2017/digital/news/verizon-yahoo-data-hacks-350-million-deal-1201992682/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare Data Breaches Up 40% Since 2015&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;She was placed on administrative leave in 2016. But the Miami-based safety net health system is certainly not alone in experiencing data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.healthleadersmedia.com/technology/healthcare-data-breaches-40-2015&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.healthleadersmedia.com/technology/healthcare-data-breaches-40-2015&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cyberattacks a top concern of businesses worldwide, survey finds&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cyberattacks, followed by data breaches and unplanned IT and telecom outages are the leading causes of concern regarding operations among &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://thehill.com/policy/cybersecurity/320450-cyberattacks-top-concerns-of-businesses-worldwide-survey-finds&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://thehill.com/policy/cybersecurity/320450-cyberattacks-top-concerns-of-businesses-worldwide-survey-finds&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon, Yahoo slash merger deal by $350M over data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some analysts had expressed concerns that Verizon could have assumed Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s liabilities over the data breaches. And reports last week said &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://thehill.com/policy/technology/320481-verizon-yahoo-slash-merger-deal-by-350m-over-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://thehill.com/policy/technology/320481-verizon-yahoo-slash-merger-deal-by-350m-over-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

