&lt;p&gt;data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://origin-nyi.thehill.com/policy/technology/320481-verizon-yahoo-slash-merger-deal-by-350m-over-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://origin-nyi.thehill.com/policy/technology/320481-verizon-yahoo-slash-merger-deal-by-350m-over-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Retrace Log Management Combines Logs, Errors, and Code Level Performance&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;integrating application logs and errors together with APM transaction &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://stackify.com/log-management/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://stackify.com/log-management/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo and Verizon said to cut merger price by $350 million&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The agreement had faced many headwinds, from multiple Yahoo data breaches to circulating rumors about Verizon asking for a huge discount on the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.consumeraffairs.com/news/yahoo-and-verizon-said-to-cut-merger-price-by-350-million-022117.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.consumeraffairs.com/news/yahoo-and-verizon-said-to-cut-merger-price-by-350-million-022117.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon Getting 7% Discount on Yahoo After Massive Hacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Verizon is getting a 7% discount on its purchase of Yahoo after the latter revealed massive data breaches that resulted in the information of more than &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.newser.com/story/238697/verizon-getting-7-discount-on-yahoo-after-massive-hacks.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.newser.com/story/238697/verizon-getting-7-discount-on-yahoo-after-massive-hacks.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo Shareholders Sue Over Massive Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Law360, New York (February 21, 2017, 4:33 PM EST) &amp;ndash; A group of Yahoo Inc. shareholders has filed a derivative complaint in Delaware Chancery &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.law360.com/consumerprotection/articles/893976/yahoo-shareholders-sue-over-massive-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.law360.com/consumerprotection/articles/893976/yahoo-shareholders-sue-over-massive-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Whitepaper: Consumer Class Actions Arising from Data Breaches Present a&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Announcements of data breaches quickly turn the gears of the court system, as class action attorneys waste little time in acting upon the potential &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.vorys.com/publications-1933.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.vorys.com/publications-1933.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

